             </item>
             <item>
              <widget class="QCheckBox" name="chkRecursiveGallery">
               <property name="toolTip">
                <string>勾选后将搜索子目录下的图片文件。默认关闭以提高性能。</string>
               </property>
               <property name="text">
                <string>递归扫描图库子文件夹 / Recursive Scan for Gallery</string>
